data.meta_description: biografia de ingles- shakira - Free download as Powerpoint Presentation (.ppt / .pptx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This biography provides details about Shakira, including her real name of Shakira Isabel Mebarak Ripoll, height of 1.57 meters, birthdate of February 2, 1977, occupation as a singer and artist, marital status of engaged, birthplace of Barranquilla, Colombia, current residence of Barcelona, and information that she is the creator of the Barefoot Foundation and enjoys seafood.
